geneVariantDescriptions.description: ERBB2 (HER2) positive indicates the presence of the ERBB2 (HER2) gene, mRNA, and/or protein. ERBB2 (HER2) positive has been used alternatively to refer to overexpression and/or amplification of ERBB2 (HER2). For related data, refer to ERBB2 amp or ERBB2 overexp in CKB.
